### Test Cookie Authentication

### 1. Login with Cookies
POST https://localhost:5001/api/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "Pa$$w0rd"
}

### 2. Test Admin Endpoint with Cookie (should work automatically)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/buggy/admin-secret
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get User Info with Cookie
GET https://localhost:5001/api/account/user-info
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Logout (clears cookie)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/account/logout
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Test Admin Endpoint after logout (should fail)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/buggy/admin-secret
Content-Type: application/json
